wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.CN.def: Inventories are stocks of goods held by firms to meet temporary or unexpected fluctuations in production or sales, and "work in progress." Data are in current local currency.
wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.CN.name: Changes in inventories
wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.CN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
